  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research project is a multi-center double-blind, parallel, randomized, controlled
      clinical trial design comparing the efficacy of dental scaling and root planing to control
      treatment (superficial cleaning) for the prevention of preterm birth in pregnant women with
      periodontal disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
